Pick your favorite LUCKY LEAF(R) Premium Pie Filling: Apple, Cherry or Blueberry. Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Place two cans of pie filling in bottom of 9x13-inch pan. Blend softened butter, oatmeal, brown sugar and nuts until crumbly. Now's the time to add in anything else you'd like to include in your crisp.* Sprinkle mixture over pie filling. Bake for 30 minutes or until golden brown. *ADD IN YOUR FAVORITES: coconut, chocolate chips, cinnamon chips, dried fruit, etc. The options are endless and the choice is yours!